1:19:57.092 --> 1:19:57.891
They were standing right there.

1:19:59.395 --> 1:20:00.394
I talked to them.

1:20:01.831 --> 1:20:03.063
- Who, honey?

1:20:03.900 --> 1:20:05.199
- Papo and MeMaw.

1:20:08.004 --> 1:20:09.236
They hugged me and,

1:20:11.007 --> 1:20:14.909
and said they were fine,
that they loved me.

1:20:14.911 --> 1:20:17.144
And then MeMaw said
that I had to come back

1:20:17.146 --> 1:20:19.914
because y'all needed me.

1:20:22.952 --> 1:20:25.820
They had cocktail
glasses in their hands

1:20:25.822 --> 1:20:27.454
like it was happy hour.

1:20:29.025 --> 1:20:30.357
I felt Papo's breath.

1:20:32.061 --> 1:20:35.229
It smelled like warm whiskey.

1:20:36.465 --> 1:20:39.200
- I told you, Papo's breath.

1:20:39.202 --> 1:20:42.069
- And I smelled MeMaw's
perfume, like two rose bushes

1:20:42.071 --> 1:20:43.070
and a honeysuckle.

1:20:45.308 --> 1:20:50.077
And I looked back and
they raised their glasses.

1:20:51.380 --> 1:20:52.613
They had crushed ice.

1:20:56.118 --> 1:20:58.485
- Mom, I love you, I'm
so glad you're not dead.

1:20:58.487 --> 1:21:00.521
But you gotta hear this.

1:21:02.291 --> 1:21:06.427
According to this, Papo has
executed your wishes, Mom.

1:21:06.429 --> 1:21:11.065
This is from Jeanne Anne,
March 24, 2003, to Papo.

1:21:12.268 --> 1:21:14.268
I think you should read it, Dad.

1:21:16.939 --> 1:21:19.406
(gentle music)

1:21:22.979 --> 1:21:26.113
- Dear Daddy, I thought
about our last discussion

1:21:26.115 --> 1:21:28.949
and I've come to the
following conclusion.

1:21:28.951 --> 1:21:31.352
Jimmy is the most understanding,

1:21:33.289 --> 1:21:37.057
warm loving husband
a woman could have.

1:21:41.264 --> 1:21:43.163
But I feel his
frustration with me.

1:21:44.600 --> 1:21:47.501
I wish I could be the
open, playful partner

1:21:47.503 --> 1:21:51.138
that Jimmy needs, but I'm
just not a free spirit.

1:21:53.476 --> 1:21:56.644
I love Jimmy more than
anything or anyone.

1:21:56.646 --> 1:21:57.912
And I always have.

1:21:59.548 --> 1:22:03.450
Please promise me that if I
ever receive any inheritance,

1:22:03.452 --> 1:22:07.054
I would like it all to
go to Jimmy, all of it.

1:22:08.357 --> 1:22:10.491
Maybe then he'll realize
how much I really love him.

1:22:11.494 --> 1:22:13.560
I know you'll honor my wish.

1:22:13.562 --> 1:22:15.429
Thank you for always
being there for me.

1:22:17.333 --> 1:22:19.199
Your loving daughter,
Jeanne Anne.

1:22:21.337 --> 1:22:24.204
- Well, I'll be damned if a
drought didn't end with a flood.

1:22:25.207 --> 1:22:27.374
You gave him the ranch, baby.

1:22:29.245 --> 1:22:31.578
- Hell honey, I mean, I
don't know what to say.

1:22:33.015 --> 1:22:35.149
You can have it
back, I believe you.

1:22:36.152 --> 1:22:39.386
- I don't want it back.

1:22:39.388 --> 1:22:42.556
I want you to know how
much I really do love you.

1:22:44.994 --> 1:22:45.993
And I always have.

1:22:51.033 --> 1:22:55.035
There is not a material
possession, amount of money,

1:22:55.037 --> 1:22:58.372
or secret fishing hole
than can ever express

1:22:58.374 --> 1:23:01.208
how much I do love you.

1:23:02.244 --> 1:23:04.979
I love this.
(laughing)

1:23:05.681 --> 1:23:08.349
- So do I.
(laughing)

1:23:12.221 --> 1:23:13.620
- But then it doesn't hurt.

1:23:16.292 --> 1:23:19.293
I want you to have it
all and run that ranch,

1:23:19.295 --> 1:23:20.761
just like Papo did.

1:23:22.264 --> 1:23:23.731
- And we'll run it
as one big family,

1:23:23.733 --> 1:23:26.333
Sallie and Juan included.

1:23:27.136 --> 1:23:29.303
- I really do love this family.

1:23:29.305 --> 1:23:32.306
- Wait, Dad, there's more.

1:23:37.446 --> 1:23:39.713
- Okay, Papo wants
us to do a toast.

1:23:39.715 --> 1:23:41.115
Grab your glasses.

1:23:41.117 --> 1:23:42.282
- Oh!
- Are you kidding me?

1:23:47.556 --> 1:23:51.425
- A toast, to love,
health, wealth,

1:23:51.427 --> 1:23:53.727
and plenty of time to enjoy it.

1:23:53.729 --> 1:23:55.696
- [All] To love, health, wealth,

1:23:55.698 --> 1:23:58.298
and plenty of time
to enjoy them.

1:23:58.300 --> 1:24:02.202
