1:24:20.756 --> 1:24:22.222
this side of the dirt.

1:24:25.061 --> 1:24:26.527
- This side of the star dirt.

1:24:31.333 --> 1:24:32.266
- Oh baby, I love you.

1:24:36.172 --> 1:24:38.472
- I love you guys, man.

1:24:38.474 --> 1:24:40.641
- I love you, big boy.

